      "post": {
        "summary": "Initiates the card setup process for Stripe.  Returns an object that can be used \r\nclient-side to create the card for the customer.  If the logged-in customer hasn't\r\nyet had an account created for them on Stripe's end, we'll make that call in this\r\nmethod as well.",
