      "post": {
        "summary": "Creates an authorization token for a customer (i.e., logs the user in) by redeeming\r\na transfer token.  The intended use here is for an older customer-facing app to generate\r\na token for a logged-in user, then this version of the API uses that token to log the\r\nuser in to the new app.",
        "operationId": "CustomerPublic_LoginViaToken",
        "tags": [
