      "post": {
        "summary": "Creates a student and also accepts the profile image (if specified) at the same time.\r\nThe incoming request must be encoded as \"multipart/form-data\" with two entries.  The\r\nfirst should be named \"studentInfo\" and should be a JSON-encoded string containing\r\nthe student record.  The second should be the actual image file (if specified).",
